title: GIVEAWAY - Das Keyboard 4 Ultimate - A beautiful and well-priced mechanical keyboard
description:
I'm giving away a beautiful Das Keyboard 4 Ultimate!  http://daskeyboard.com (P.S. I get paid nothing from Das Keyboard for this video)  Das Keyboard makes some amazing mechanical keyboards that are a pleasure to type on all day.  The 4 Ultimate has an anodized aluminum top and Cherry MX keyswitches, which, when combined, makes for an incredible typing experience.  The Das Keyboard Ultimate also features blank keycaps to promote more efficient typing (that's right, MORE efficient...because it breaks terrible habits)

View the 4 Ultimate at http://www.daskeyboard.com/daskeyboard-4-ultimate/
